      "comment": "SCOTT GREYSCALE (8) ran the fastest on the card last time scoring by 6 lengths (26.05) at this track. Rates a top chance again. DOONGALLA GEM (6) goes very well here including two wins. Missed the frame latest (26.42) when sixth over 450m at Ballarat in a Grade 5. Among the main chances. HEATHCOTE RUPEE (3) failed to feature last start after drifting back at Warrnambool, but prior to that won by 1.5 lengths at Warragul (22.93) beating Borroloola Boy in a Grade 5 on June 20. Goes well out of this box with a win and two minor placings. Should be in this for a long way. KID GULLA (4) jumps at a shorter journey and still warrants respect.",
